description: Retrieves the current settings of the IoT Analytics logging options.

nested_items.name: loggingOptions
nested_items.description: The current settings of the IoT Analytics logging options.

nested_items.name: roleArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the role that grants permission to IoT Analytics to perform logging.

nested_items.name: level
nested_items.description: The logging level. Currently, only ERROR is supported.

nested_items.name: enabled
nested_items.description: If true, logging is enabled for IoT Analytics.
